data.description: Welcome to 471 Clarion Road, a charming and spacious home located in the desirable Westchester Commons neighborhood of Lawrenceville. This stunning property offers a perfect balance of modern amenities and classic architectural details with many upgrades like newer roof and brand new energy star rated windows throughout! As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting and open floor plan. The main level features a spacious living room with large windows, filling the space with natural light. The adjacent dining area is perfect for hosting family gatherings or entertaining guests. The kitchen is a true chef's delight, equipped with modern appliances, ample counter space, and plenty of storage. Prepare delicious meals while enjoying views of the backyard through the bay window. Upstairs, you'll find the private living quarters. The primary bedroom is a peaceful retreat, with a spacious layout, an en-suite bathroom, and its own fireplace. Two additional well-appointed bedrooms provide flexibility for a growing family or guests. The backyard is a true oasis. Spend sunny afternoons lounging on the patio, hosting barbecues, or playing games with loved ones. The expansive yard offers endless possibilities for gardening, outdoor activities, or even adding a pool. Located in Lawrenceville, this home offers easy access to shopping, dining, and entertainment options. With its convenient proximity to major highways, commuting to nearby cities or downtown Atlanta is a breeze. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful house your new home. Schedule a showing today and experience the best of Lawrenceville living!
